{"tid":700863,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"狂賀!發電新能源","createTime":"2018-06-13T16:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T16:49:55.000Z","uid":137017,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3428cfb1d14b2d84c661f9cea1c41c14788c7d","tid":700863,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"係呢個資源匱乏嘅年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，竟然俾我呢個天才發現左發電的新能源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而呢個新能源就係... ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健身室班大隻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢哋日日操練過程中消耗大量能量，如果轉化成發電的驅動力，中電港燈仲唔收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68440832764cebbdb423d16e6fd3355790848121","tid":700863,"uid":55232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"嗯 早啲訓啦7頭"},{"pid":"84db721c3db1532c0bc10f21c0c12a7eed7785e9","tid":700863,"uid":65587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/004259_12b70d14cde428ae32e6476ec81dd26d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F004259_12b70d14cde428ae32e6476ec81dd26d.gif&h=af8eb9c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31a0c710d8616a94e9c27548b1c060f153a118f","tid":700863,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"巴西監獄推行「發電減刑」　踩腳踏車16小時少關1天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n巴西聯邦監獄最近才推行「讀書減刑」規定，讓犯人讀1本書減刑4天。位於聖利塔都薩普卡伊市(Santa Rita do Sapucai)的監獄也推行「發電減刑」，只要受刑人以人力發電的方式踩腳踏車16個小時，就能夠為自己減刑1天！<br />\n<br />\n▼巴西監獄推出「發電減刑」，大家都卯起來踩腳踏車。(圖／取自網路)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/113/d113814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F113%2Fd113814.jpg&h=38946a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獄方表示，「發電減刑」一來可讓犯人活動筋骨，消耗多餘的精力；二來又能讓他們即使在監獄裡，也能回饋社會。這些由腳踏車產生的電力將會統一匯聚到市政中心，再分配給附近區域的路燈照明等公共設施使用。<br />\n<br />\n提出建議的法官說，這項減刑措施一開始乏人問津，可是後來參加的人越來越多，原先設置的10輛腳踏車早就不夠用了，預計還會再增添8輛。有受刑人則說，自從「發電減刑」規定推行後，他每天都為了提早出獄而去踩腳踏車，現在已經瘦了4公斤了！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120703/69392.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20120703%2F69392.htm&d=wPOOKsuVFudhTjFSvVoaSROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c6c3e488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20120703/69392.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a3bc7fdaaac5c5db20d94a9b56f7c18380303888","tid":700863,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}